  "id": "RAW_d8c2e0a4",
  "title": "孤独比疾病更致命，而 AI 正在解决它 | 融资 700 万美元的 Newdays 会带来哪些变化？",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzAxMDMxOTI2NA==&mid=2649101239&idx=1&sn=e7631f0384c969378357a58051692885",
  "date": "2025-11-21 11:13:00",
  "author": "十字路口Crossing",
  "siteName": "十字路口Crossing",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <blockquote style=\"border-top:none;padding:10px;margin:20px 0px;border-right:none;display:block;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;border-bottom:none;word-spacing:normal;outline:0px;overflow:auto;border-left:8px solid rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;hyphens:auto;text-align:left;\">\n    <div style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n     <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"word-break:break-all;font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;blockquote&quot;,{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;normal&quot;,&quot;editId&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;nickname&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;authorName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;from&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;line-height: 26px;word-spacing: normal;hyphens: auto;text-align: left;outline: 0px;margin: 20px 0px;border-top: none;border-right: none;border-bottom: none;display: block;overflow: auto;padding: 10px;border-left: 8px solid rgb(34, 34, 34);background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, \\&quot;Times New Roman\\&quot;, serif;font-size: 15px;&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-size: 15px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;padding-left: 0em;font-size: 15px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;word-break: break-all;font-weight: 600;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">为什么是对话？为什么是 AI？</span></span></p>\n    </div>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p></p>\n   <figure style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"loading\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"501617481\" data-ratio=\"0.5009259259259259\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"border-radius: 10px;font-size: 15px;height: auto !important;\" width=\"100%\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=705f65a7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FFFcNSoQ3KictH3FrHpChkw0T1tXqDHMFuPmUibFiaNrruEYuWxD6ZowBMBYn4tx97shIfSibia82qNzAzSSV2Z9CyWQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:right;\"><span leaf=\"\">👦🏻 作者: Bella Qiao</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:right;\"><span leaf=\"\">🥷 编辑: Koji</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:right;\"><span leaf=\"\">🧑‍🎨 排版: NCon</span></p>\n   <figure style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"loading\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.12129629629629629\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"border-radius: 10px;font-size: 15px;height: auto !important;\" width=\"100%\" data-imgfileid=\"501617478\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2fb05020&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FFFcNSoQ3KictH3FrHpChkw0T1tXqDHMFuTlUIz7rBiafDCemkGaPkTXCZJW9hkVd5nZ5UdPFspaiaEGnsJwuN3icoA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">全球数亿人正面临认知衰退的困扰，催生了一个医疗支出高达数万亿的“无解”市场。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">当大多数 AI 公司还在虚拟社交的红海中竞争时，</span><span style=\"word-break:break-all;font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">由前 Google Glass 负责人巴巴克·帕维兹（Babak Parviz）和工程师丹尼尔·凯利（Daniel Kelly）创立的 NewDays AI，选择了将 AI 陪伴用于延缓认知衰退。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">2025 年 9 月，公司完成了由 General Catalyst 和 Madrona Venture Group 共同领投的 700 万美元种子轮融资。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">投资人看中的，不只是他们的技术背景和个人使命感，更是一个覆盖数亿人口、万亿美元级的银发健康市场。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">NewDays AI 选择了一条更难但价值巨大的路：将 AI 陪伴从“情感慰藉”升级为一种经临床验证的“数字疗法”，用以干预和延缓认知衰退。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">他们的商业逻辑很简单：既然高频的结构化对话能有效刺激大脑，那为什么不用 AI 来实现这种高成本疗法的普惠化？</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">在「十字路口」，我们一直关注 AI 带来的行业变革。本文将深度拆解 NewDays 如何将严肃科学、AI 技术与创新的商业模式结合，试图撬动庞大的银发健康市场。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"word-break:break-all;font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这不仅是一家公司的故事，更是 AI 如何在“科技与人文的十字路口”创造真实价值的经典案例。</span></span></p>\n   <figure style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"loading\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"501617479\" data-ratio=\"0.7240740740740741\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"border-radius: 10px;font-size: 15px;height: auto !important;\" width=\"100%\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=24f2104c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FFFcNSoQ3KictH3FrHpChkw0T1tXqDHMFuB1Eq90JRuCZyPfG0ZRUAIDWHia8uz2NsJkiaZpsjlR9uj4iaibt70Q4vibw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <h2 style=\"padding:0px 0.2em;margin:40px auto;font-weight:bold;width:fit-content;font-size:20px;line-height:1.5;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果大脑能重塑，AI 能否让疗法普惠？</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">在全球范围内，65 岁以上人群中大约有 5%～8% 患有痴呆症，而大约 10%～20% 有轻度认知衰退（MCI）。</span></p>\n   <figure style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"loading\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"501617480\" data-ratio=\"0.6157407407407407\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"border-radius: 10px;font-size: 15px;height: auto !important;\" width=\"100%\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3e51b13c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FFFcNSoQ3KictH3FrHpChkw0T1tXqDHMFu3FbQmUtLNFuO7qElRvoEBPpYdbPCMFmHfycp4tsJvq44UExWvxqCiag%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">痴呆患者的医疗支出往往是普通老人的</span><span style=\"word-break:break-all;font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">三倍</span></span><span leaf=\"\">。对于患者和家庭来说，随之而来的经济和情感压力，更是难以想象。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">然而，真正的悲剧在于，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">社会已经习惯了对痴呆症的“无解”</span>。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">对许多认知衰退患者及其家属来说，医生能给出的建议往往只有一句：“保持健康的生活习惯”。除此之外，他们只能无奈地等着病情恶化。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">从市场角度看，这并非“小问题”。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">全球已有超 5,500 万人患有痴呆，每年新增近千万病例，美国的相关支出已超过 3,000 亿美元，预计 2050 年将突破万亿。<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">更庞大的 MCI 群体几乎没有有效干预手段，这意味着一个覆盖数亿人口、万亿美元级别的空白市场。</span></span></p>\n   <h2 style=\"padding:0px 0.2em;margin:40px auto;font-weight:bold;width:fit-content;font-size:20px;line-height:1.5;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\">NewDays 的答案</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">NewDays 想要打破这种无力感。他们认为，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">认知健康应该像心血管健康一样，被纳入日常健康管理。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">而事实也证明：轻度认知衰退并非完全不可逆，它是可以被干预、被延缓的。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">过去 20 年，超过 300 项随机对照临床试验证实：认知干预有效。其背后的关键科学原理，是神经可塑性（neuroplasticity）。</span></p>\n   <figure style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"loading\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"501617482\" data-ratio=\"0.5953703703703703\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"border-radius: 10px;font-size: 15px;height: auto !important;\" width=\"100%\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=08838d60&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FFFcNSoQ3KictH3FrHpChkw0T1tXqDHMFuD4vqvdJku3ibrlqzVK327rFseA2z9ED97xK3dKsXMKgpqurUAkf9zjg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-style: italic;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">（图片来源于 General Catalyst)</span></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">就像中风患者通过康复训练可以重新学会说话一样，大脑在任何年龄都具有“可塑性”。只要有足够的刺激和训练，大脑就能重建新的神经连接，从而改善记忆、注意力、等等。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">NewDays 的核心方法论，正是基于一项由哈佛大学 Dodge 教授主导的研究成果——</span><span style=\"word-break:break-all;font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">I-CONECT</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;项目。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">I-CONECT 是一个“对话式干预”实验。研究对象是 75 岁以上、长期处于社会隔离状态的老人。研究团队安排他们每周与经过训练的临床人员进行多次结构化对话，坚持 6～12 个月。</span></p>\n   <figure style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"loading\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6916666666666667\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"border-radius: 10px;font-size: 15px;height: auto !important;\" width=\"100%\" data-imgfileid=\"501617484\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=37b69607&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FFFcNSoQ3KictH3FrHpChkw0T1tXqDHMFu9qmybdI8meKiaAnDUISsibQibJl3QIcZKru1vC8nlnD5vPFjWmBZzxD8Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">结果非常令人振奋：<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">参与者的 MoCA （认知评估）分数显著提升，记忆和语言能力都有改善，脑部影像甚至显示出与注意力相关的神经网络连通性增强。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">而 ACTIVE 临床试验也发现：仅 6 周的认知训练，在 10 年后仍有长期效果。尤其是处理速度训练组，痴呆风险降低了 29%。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">这些研究都说明了，虽然痴呆症无法被完全治愈，但能这些项目可以显著改善老人的生活质量、延缓症状恶化，在最佳情况下能将症状推迟数月甚至更久。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">很可惜的是，而是这种密集型干预模式由于高昂的人力成本，几乎无法大规模推广。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">但&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Newdays 的创始人认为，Gen AI 能让这类预防性治疗变得更加普惠。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">NewDays 已经拿到 I-CONECT 协议的独家许可。这构成了 NewDays 最重要的资产之一：</span><span style=\"word-break:break-all;font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">基于严肃临床研究的独家疗法协议</span></span><span leaf=\"\">。相比于还在探索产品市场契合度（PMF）的通用陪聊应用，NewDays 从第一天起就拥有清晰的、经过验证的干预路径。这让它拥有别人难以复制的优势。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">这种人与 AI 结合的方案，使得密集型的临床性对话这一繁琐的部分交给 AI 陪伴 。而医生则在关键时刻介入：<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">负责评估病情、监督进展，并提供个性化的治疗建议。</span></span></p>\n   <figure style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"loading\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"501617483\" data-ratio=\"0.5925925925925926\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"border-radius: 10px;font-size: 15px;height: auto !important;\" width=\"100%\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2f7976cf&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FFFcNSoQ3KictH3FrHpChkw0T1tXqDHMFu6v1dATXLbWcuA1EsTvicYZX5PkkUo6oCsJQ7ib6G1q3KUMUPB4L6beUA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">换句话说，Newdays 正在把与临床人员对话转化为 与 AI 对话。这样让本来稀缺且昂贵的疗法，有了走向大众化的可能。</span></p>\n   <h2 style=\"padding:0px 0.2em;margin:40px auto;font-weight:bold;width:fit-content;font-size:20px;line-height:1.5;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\">Newdays 的产品模式：AI 干预+ 医生评估的结合体</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">在 Newdays，认知健康管理分为三步：</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"word-break:break-all;font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">第一，AI 陪伴Sunny 会先行介入。</span></span></p>\n   <figure style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"loading\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"501617485\" data-ratio=\"0.9537037037037037\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"border-radius: 10px;font-size: 15px;height: auto !important;\" width=\"100%\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8bce0d0c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FFFcNSoQ3KictH3FrHpChkw0T1tXqDHMFuOup8FUQFUgfk5u9AvHXQ1VmTFib8ictsqApXRhBrlag2RoR0KO8fFM8g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">用户会通过日对话练习、认知刺激活动，在没有门槛的情况下先体验、建立与 AI 陪伴对话的习惯。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI 陪伴 Sunny 有时会引导用户回忆以前的经历，有时则带领他们进行更具体的认知训练，比如要求用户记住几个特定的词，并把它们用在一句话里。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Sunny 可以做到与用户高频互动，帮助他们维持社交与认知活跃度。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"word-break:break-all;font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">第二，医生会进行对用户的认知做评估。</span></span></p>\n   <figure style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"loading\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"501617487\" data-ratio=\"0.9175925925925926\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"border-radius: 10px;font-size: 15px;height: auto !important;\" width=\"100%\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=062576d7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FFFcNSoQ3KictH3FrHpChkw0T1tXqDHMFuXnSv4GbNDxz87IMUu50vhIG2tVBcmHJQC8BUuzTYn1hQAwEtXhhxiaQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">通过一次性的视频问诊，医生会听取用户的担忧、了解风险因素，并给出个性化的建议。这样就把 AI 的日常陪伴和医生的专业诊断衔接起来。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"word-break:break-all;font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">第三，用户可选择成为长期会员。</span></span></p>\n   <figure style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"loading\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.950925925925926\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"border-radius: 10px;font-size: 15px;height: auto !important;\" width=\"100%\" data-imgfileid=\"501617486\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6a008803&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FFFcNSoQ3KictH3FrHpChkw0T1tXqDHMFuZxqicLtTyJalP0MfkPPoG3FkEglpXLEd9KRaOj2pcT7lyC5TjwibpzTQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果用户选择成为会员，将会获得个性化的治疗方案，以及与clinician的定期视频通话。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">NewDays 的会员每月收费 99 美元，而临床视频会诊可以走保险。这是一种“医疗收费 + 数字订阅”的混合模式。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">NewDays 还配备了一支内部临床医生团队（不包含在月费中），负责监督患者的整体照护，并向 AI 系统提供反馈。</span></p>\n   <h2 style=\"padding:0px 0.2em;margin:40px auto;font-weight:bold;width:fit-content;font-size:20px;line-height:1.5;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\">NewDays 投资人的愿景与医疗体系布局</span></h2>\n   <figure style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;\">\n    <span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:1.5px;display:inline !important;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;float:none;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:left;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\">2025年 9 月 3 日，Newdays AI 已完成了 700 万美元的种子轮投资。这次融资由 General Catalyst 和 Madrona Venture Group 共同领投。</span></span>\n   </figure>\n  </div>\n  <div data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <figure style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"loading\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"501617489\" data-ratio=\"0.5333333333333333\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"border-radius: 10px;font-size: 15px;height: auto !important;\" width=\"100%\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=08f50ce8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FFFcNSoQ3KictH3FrHpChkw0T1tXqDHMFuahtJJjz9diaEfnMYKYGfKAuGRP4F1P7FIyaOib5wWTDdtkn2zxahJU6Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-style: italic;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">（图片来源于网络）</span></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">投资人看中的，不只是技术与团队，更是一个巨大的社会需求：人口的老龄化和痴呆症的医疗负担。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">General Catalyst 的长期命题叫 Health Assurance——是把医疗从“救火的的 sick care”转成“主动、普惠”的日常照护体系。</span></p>\n   <figure style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"loading\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"501617491\" data-ratio=\"1.1092592592592592\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"border-radius: 10px;font-size: 15px;height: auto !important;\" width=\"100%\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=65a47efe&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FFFcNSoQ3KictH3FrHpChkw0T1tXqDHMFu3kytjGbucbZJMiapUrPqHf3AKYxYbNbOpU9oqDoSQCAKj98M6wJnJaw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">老龄化与认知衰退，正是验证这一命题的的最好场景。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">传统的老龄看护往往依赖机构，而新的趋势正走向居家化 + 数字化（phygital） 的连续干预。。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">而 NewDays 把“高频对话式的认知干预”做成 AI 陪伴+ 临床指导的混合服务，既能规模化，又能保持医疗的严谨性，正好呼应 GC 的愿景。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">更重要的是，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">GC 不只是投资一家公司，而是在搭建整个“变革底座”。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">比如，它通过旗下 HATCo 推动对 Summa Health 的并购（已在 2025 年 6 月获俄亥俄州总检长有条件批准），这是 VC 直接持有医院系统的破局之举。</span></p>\n   <figure style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"loading\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"501617490\" data-ratio=\"0.6138888888888889\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"border-radius: 10px;font-size: 15px;height: auto !important;\" width=\"100%\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4a1cff72&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FFFcNSoQ3KictH3FrHpChkw0T1tXqDHMFuESpW4ibjYIlJz4hTgkcCMQ97pBv5t7uRHRIKv1loux3o52mlzQMSPkQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">对 Newdays 来说，他们借助 GC 已经铺好的医院资源，就能更快融入医生的日常流程，也能拿到更真实、更有说服力的临床数据。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">而产品的效果，也可以和医院的硬指标来衡量。一旦这些数据证明了新方法在成本效益上的优势，Newdays 就能从单点试运行，扩展到整个医疗体系，顺势走向规模化。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">目前为止，很多 “AI 陪伴” 产品容易陷入同质化。Newdays 与其他 AI 陪伴的差距在于疗法协议与临床证据。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">NewDays 已经拿到了 I-CONECT 协议的独家许可。这意味着，它把“高频、结构化对话就是认知刺激”这一经由随机对照验证的路径，真正做成了产品。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">这也是为什么，在 GC 的投资稿里，NewDays 被定义为‘证据驱动的干预’，而不是一个内容聊天工具。</span></p>\n   <figure style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"loading\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"501617492\" data-ratio=\"0.6277777777777778\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"border-radius: 10px;font-size: 15px;height: auto !important;\" width=\"100%\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=41665a43&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FFFcNSoQ3KictH3FrHpChkw0T1tXqDHMFunHYib6qjXuEbDDiaiaHiaplbhxekBlqat0UlF897eavowFCXoLpQv5z7bw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">有了这一层临床正当性，NewDays 在合规、伦理、医保谈判，甚至品牌信任上，都比泛陪聊产品更有话语权。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">早期测试反馈也很好：用户满意度高达 4.8/5，所有参与者都表示自己“感觉更好”。</span></p>\n   <figure style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"loading\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"501617488\" data-ratio=\"0.45\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"border-radius: 10px;font-size: 15px;height: auto !important;\" width=\"100%\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1d149878&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FFFcNSoQ3KictH3FrHpChkw0T1tXqDHMFuel6WYhyJZBhn8LNz6zEG5SgXQuDq1zte1y97wmicXF0KUzZ11Lhm2eQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">这让人看见了 AI 的另一种可能：不是制造幻象的陪伴，而是把真正有效的干预，带到更多人的日常生活里。</span></p>\n   <h2 style=\"padding:0px 0.2em;margin:40px auto;font-weight:bold;width:fit-content;font-size:20px;line-height:1.5;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\">Newdays 创始人背后的故事</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">NewDays AI 由两位联合创始人共同建立：</span><span style=\"word-break:break-all;font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">CEO 巴巴克·帕维兹（Babak Parviz）和首席创新官丹尼尔·凯利（Daniel Kelly）。</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;他们不仅有深厚的技术背景，也都因为家族经历，与认知障碍有着切身的共鸣。</span></p>\n   <figure style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"loading\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7379629629629629\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"border-radius: 10px;font-size: 15px;height: auto !important;\" width=\"100%\" data-imgfileid=\"501617495\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1671dd74&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FFFcNSoQ3KictH3FrHpChkw0T1tXqDHMFupsLIRtWVOxjFZAIC23QtAFcrVBVGeOzxKV0iav8kIRpWYia4LUMspaIg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">帕维兹的履历堪称传奇：他</span><span style=\"word-break:break-all;font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">曾在 Google X 领导 Google Glass 项目</span></span><span leaf=\"\">，并推动机器人手术和智能隐形眼镜的研发。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">在 亚马逊 担任副总裁期间，</span><span style=\"word-break:break-all;font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">他创立了“Grand Challenge”部门，专注于探索公司未来的新业务，其中就包括老龄化与医疗。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">离开亚马逊后，他又加入 Madrona VC，继续深耕人工智能与医疗交叉的投资。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">凯利则长期专注于工程与医疗的结合。但更重要的是，认知障碍在他的家庭中带来了深刻的烙印——他父亲的五个兄弟姐妹都曾患有痴呆，所以他比大多数人更理解这种疾病对家庭的冲击。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">帕维兹同样有类似的经历：</span><span style=\"word-break:break-all;font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">他的父亲多年与阿尔茨海默症抗争。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">他很清楚阿尔茨海默症无法治愈，但研究结果让他看到希望：认知训练和在临床医生引导下的对话，在某些情况下能够改善痴呆症状。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">这份希望，也成为他创立 NewDays、打造 AI 陪伴 Sunny 的起点。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">但值得注意的是，这些研究里的“陪伴”都是人类专业人员完成的，而不是 AI。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">哈佛商学院 Ethical Intelligence Lab 的主任 Dr. Julian De Freitas 就提出：换成 AI 之后，效果可能会不一样。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">目前，</span><span style=\"word-break:break-all;font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">NewDays 还没有开展过自己的临床研究。不过，帕维兹表示，Sunny 的对话已经非常接近人类，他们 “有相当的信心” 结果会类似于已有研究。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">但这更多是一种信念，而非已经拿出的数据。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">比起“改善认知”，</span><span style=\"word-break:break-all;font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI 在缓解孤独上的作用更有实证支持。对很多老年人来说，孤独感本身就是一个沉重的问题，无论是否存在认知障碍。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">在这一点上，AI 陪伴的潜力已经有了更明确的证据支持。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Dr. De Freitas 的研究也发现：</span><span style=\"word-break:break-all;font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">至少对健康成年人来说，和一个有同理心的聊天机器人对话，减轻孤独感的效果，几乎不亚于和一个陌生人面对面交谈。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">或许 AI 陪伴 能不能“治病”还要等更多数据来证明，但在减少孤独感上，它已经展现出清晰的价值。</span></p>\n   <figure style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"loading\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"501617493\" data-ratio=\"0.3648148148148148\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"border-radius: 10px;font-size: 15px;height: auto !important;\" width=\"100%\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3e543792&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FFFcNSoQ3KictH3FrHpChkw0T1tXqDHMFuQNic1GcRuCFQAGMJpKGMELDzjuaNwjXhKFocbSdoWudjk7jxiaibfzTPQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <p style=\"margin:10px 0px;white-space:pre-line;padding-left:0em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;min-height:20px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\"> \n     <br> \n    </span></p>\n   <figure style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"loading\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4935185185185185\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"border-radius: 10px;font-size: 15px;height: auto !important;\" width=\"100%\" data-imgfileid=\"501617494\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5160890e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FFFcNSoQ3KictH3FrHpChkw0T1tXqDHMFuiaqgdqCU94cAMC8v6pSRnXIxr6fFqRibJS8lw5oUzOtPWNicLvZDKia88Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n   </figure>\n  </div>\n  <p></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章深度分析了 NewDays AI 如何将 AI 陪伴与临床验证结合，通过数字疗法延缓认知衰退，并撬动万亿美元级的银发健康市场。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章深度分析了 NewDays AI 如何将 AI 陪伴与临床验证结合，通过数字疗法延缓认知衰退，并撬动万亿美元级的银发健康市场。",
  "summary": "NewDays AI，一家由前 Google Glass 负责人创立并获得 700 万美元种子轮融资的公司，专注于将 AI 陪伴应用于延缓认知衰退，而非仅仅是虚拟社交。文章首先阐述了全球老龄化带来的认知衰退问题及其巨大的医疗支出，指出当前缺乏有效干预手段。接着，文章介绍了 NewDays AI 基于神经可塑性和 I-CONECT 项目（哈佛大学 Dodge 教授主导）的科学原理，将高成本的人力密集型对话干预转化为 AI 干预+医生评估的混合模式，实现了疗法的普惠化。文章还分析了 NewDays AI 的产品模式、投资人（General Catalyst）的愿景以及其在医疗体系中的布局，强调了 NewDays AI“证据驱动的干预”模式与泛陪聊产品的差异。最后，文章提及了创始人背景及其个人使命感，并探讨了 AI 陪伴在缓解孤独感方面的明确价值，同时也指出 AI 在“治病”效果上仍需更多数据验证。",
